item.title: CVE-2023-32467|2024-07-31T15:53:33.059Z -- dell -- powerswitch%20z9664f-on%20bios
item.description: Dell Edge Gateway BIOS, versions 3200 and 5200, contains an out-of-bounds write vulnerability. A local authenticated malicious user with high privileges could potentially exploit this vulnerability leading to exposure of some UEFI code, leading to arbitrary code execution or escalation of privilege.
